data.description: Bring your own plans on this highly desirable pair of lots ZONED RM on a soon to be recorded lot partition.  Just under 10k sf per lot with city services at the street. Home and garage are not part of purchase price. Lots to be purchased together. Duplex? Tri-plex? 4 plex? Buyer to verify all aspects of lots for their intended purpose.  Approximate 200' of street frontage across from Bonaventure on Adam st.
